## Quick Start

Install the package:

```bash
npm install @your-company/css-framework
```

Import the styles:

```scss
// In your main.scss
@import '@your-company/css-framework/scss/main';
```

## Theming

The framework supports multiple themes and color modes. You can switch between themes using the theme switcher in the top right corner of this documentation.

